{{Dialogue Start}}
;(First interaction)
::<!--Trigger PerformanceE 504056001: Config/Level/Mission/5040560/Act/Act504056001.json-->
::'''Zelos:''' Forgive my intrusion, esteemed one. I noticed you emerging from the temple, a place reserved for authorized personnel. Given your attire, you don't appear to be a regular pilgrim. May I ask who you are?
::{{DIcon|Arrow}} The Holy Maiden asked for me to be here.
:::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_504056003-->
:::'''Zelos:''' How could it be... are you a guest of the Holy Maiden?
:::'''Zelos:''' I've heard the Holy Maiden rarely shows herself in public. If she personally invited you, then you must be a priest of considerable rank! It's truly an honor to meet you!
::{{DIcon|Arrow}} I am from the future.
:::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_504056006-->
:::'''Zelos:''' The future... Are you alluding to the power of time? Could it be that you are an Oronyx priest from other cities?
:::'''Zelos:''' Ah, that would make sense. I recently learned that the Holy Maiden was expecting an esteemed guest. It's truly an honor to meet you!
::<!--Custom String Trigger: TalkSentence_504056008-->
::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_504056008-->
::'''Zelos:''' Esteemed one, though we've just met, I have a small favor to ask. Please forgive me... You've seen the Holy Maiden, so could you share what she's like?
::{{DIcon|Arrow}} Have you not seen her?
:::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_504056010-->
:::'''Zelos:''' Regrettably... I'm just a guard, and I don't have the privilege to enter the inner sanctum...
::{{DIcon|Arrow}} I know little about her myself...
:::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_504056012-->
:::'''Zelos:''' I see, well... I'm just a guard, never allowed inside the inner sanctum, so I'm curious...
::<!--Custom String Trigger: TalkSentence_504056013-->
::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_504056013-->
::'''Zelos:''' Even a few words would be appreciated. Please share!
::'''Zelos:''' Ah... just as the prophecy foretold, she truly is a kind soul. Esteemed one, please accept this token of my gratitude &mdash; consider it my humble tribute to destiny.
::{{DIcon|Arrow}} I'm afraid I can't accept this.
:::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_504056017-->
:::'''Zelos:''' Ah... I forgot you're from a foreign city. Customs here in Janusopolis must be unfamiliar to you.
::{{DIcon|Arrow}} Such generosity, isn't it?
:::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_504056019-->
:::'''Zelos:''' No, no, the fact that you didn't comment on how little it is has me on edge. Oh... I forgot you're from a foreign city, and our customs must be unfamiliar to you.
::<!--Custom String Trigger: TalkSentence_504056020-->
::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_504056020-->
::'''Zelos:''' Such integrity, esteemed one, so unlike the temple's priests... I'm deeply grateful. Noble one, if there's anything you wish to know, please feel free to inquire. I'll share everything I can!
;(Subsequent interactions)
::<!--Trigger PerformanceE 504056002: Config/Level/Mission/5040560/Act/Act504056002.json-->
::'''Zelos:''' Priest from the outlands, it's good to see you again! You look great today. Destiny must favor you! How may I assist you?
:<!--Ends the current performance-->
:<!--Open NPC Menu-->
