::{{DIcon|Talk}} What is your view on the Titan faith?
:::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_504056113-->
:::'''Zelos:''' No, no, as a mere guard, how could I dare to comment on something as sacred as a ritual? The very thought makes me uneasy...
:::'''Zelos:''' Rest assured, I heed the teachings of the priests. &mdash; {{Rubi|Janus|Passage Titan}} guides our path, and the scriptures of {{Rubi|Talanton|Law Titan}} are the foundation of every guard!
:::'''Zelos:''' Rather than that, tell me more about the Holy Maiden! What is she like? Is she truly as graceful and commanding as the prophecy foretold?
:::Considering this is the "past," revealing a little should be fine, but you don't know which Holy Maiden he's referring to, so...
