::::'''Zelos:''' Oh, a lively and spirited Holy Maiden! Even with destiny's favor, she still retains her innocence. How rare and precious!
::::<!--Custom String Trigger: TalkSentence_504056126-->
::::<!--Custom String Listener: TalkSentence_504056126-->
::::'''Zelos:''' Thank you, Honorable Priest! Your words are a blessing to me. I truly am fortunate.
